Z = (\sqrt{32} \cos \pi/4) + (\sqrt{32} \sin \pi/4)i.
\cos \pi/4 = \sin \pi/4 = \sqrt{2}/2,
Z = 4 + 4i.
r = \sqrt{x^2 + y^2}; \theta = \arctan \frac{y}{x}.
